==Ordnance Survey of Great Britain==

The [[British national grid reference system]] uses the point {{coord|49|N|2|W}} as its true origin.<ref>{{cite web|title=The true origin|url=http://www.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/oswebsite/gps/information/coordinatesystemsinfo/guidetonationalgrid/page2.html|publisher=Ordnance Survey|location=Southampton|date=2007-09-04|accessdate=2010-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205123745/http://www.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/oswebsite/gps/information/coordinatesystemsinfo/guidetonationalgrid/page2.html|archive-date=2008-12-05|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref>

