'''Gayatri Waterfalls''' is one of the many waterfalls in and around [[Nirmal]] town, along with [[Kuntala Waterfall]] and [[Pochera Falls]]. Away from the human eye, the waterfalls found its habitat in a remote place inside a deep tropical forest. It is approximately 5&nbsp;km from Tarnam Khurd, near Neredigonda of [[Adilabad district]].

