WEC |year=2000 |publisher=Orient Blackswan |ISBN=978-81-250-1871-1 |ref={{sfnref|Ray & Chattopadhyaya, A Sourcebook of Indian Civilization|2000}}}} * {{citation |last=Sharma |first=Arvind |authorlink=Arvind Sharma |title=On Hindu, Hindustan, Hinduism and Hindutva |journal=Numen |volume=49 |number=1 |year=2002 |pp=1–36 |JSTOR=3270470 |ref={{sfnref|Sharma, On Hindu, Hindustan, Hinduism and Hindutva|2002}}}} * {{citation |last=Wink |first=André |title=Al-Hind: The Making of the Indo-Islamic World |publisher=Brill |year=2002 |edition=Third |origyear=first published 1990 |ISBN=0391041738 |url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=bCVyhH5VDjAC |ref={{sfnref|Wink, Al-Hind, Volume 1|2002}}}}
