ralian Horror Films and the Limitations of Cultural Policy'], Media International Australia: Incorporating Culture and Policy, no. 133, pp.&nbsp;43–55. * Stratton, David. ''The Avocado Plantation: Boom and Bust in the Australian Film Industry''. Sydney : Pan Macmillan, 1990. 465p. {{ISBN|0-7329-0250-9}} * [[Deb Verhoeven|Verhoeven, Deb]]. ''Sheep and the Australian Cinema''. Melbourne : MUP, 2006. {{ISBN|0-522-85239-4}} * — — — ed. ''Twin Peeks: Australian and New Zealand Feature Films''. Melbourne: Damned Publishing, 1999. {{ISBN|1-876310-00-6}}
