{{unreferenced|date=April 2016}} This is a '''list of places named after [[Guangzhou]]''', [[Guangdong]], [[China]]. Most of the places are in the [[United States]] and are named after '''Canton''', the [[Guangzhou#17th through 19th centuries|more common romanisation]] for the city in the 19th and the early part of the 20th century.
