{{About|the national park|the city|Marmaris}} {{Infobox protected area | name = Marmaris National Park | alt_name = ''Marmaris Milli Parkı'' | iucn_category = | photo = | photo_alt = | photo_caption = | photo_width = | map = Turkey | map_alt = | map_caption = | map_width = | relief = yes | label = Marmaris NP | label_position = right | mark = | marker_size = | location = [[Köyceğiz]]-[[Marmaris]], [[Muğla Province]], Turkey | nearest_city = | coords = {{coord|36|50|44.83|N|28|17|52.74|E|region:TR|format=dms|display=inline,title}} | coords_ref = | area = {{convert|20206|ha|abbr=on}} | designation = | authorized = | created = | established = {{start date|1996|03|08}} | designated = | visitation_num = | visitation_year = | visitation_ref = | governing_body = [[Ministry of Forest and Water Management (Turkey)|Ministry of Forest and Water Management]] | administrator = | operator = | owner = | world_heritage_site = | website = {{URL|http://www.milliparklar.gov.tr/mp/marmaris/index.htm}} | child = | embedded = }} '''Marmaris National Park''' ({{lang-tr|Marmaris Milli Parkı}})), established on March 8, 1996, is a [[national park]] in southwestern Turkey. The national park is located in [[Köyceğiz]] and [[Marmaris]] of districts [[Muğla Province]].<ref name="mp"/>
It covers an area of {{convert|292016|ha|abbr=on}}.<ref name=mp/>
