The '''WCTC Shopping Center''' is a [[shopping mall]] in [[Koror]], [[Palau]]. It is the largest shopping mall in Palau and houses the largest department store in the country.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iexplore.com/articles/travel-guides/australia-and-south-pacific/palau/shopping-and-leisure|title=Palau — Shopping and Leisure|website=iExplore|accessdate=20 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.downtown.wphpalau.com/|title=West Plaza Hotel Downtown|website=West Plaza Hotel Downtown|accessdate=20 July 2018}}</ref>
